<doc id="148377" wikidata="Q3283001" url="?curid=148377" title="Annihilate This Week">
<text>Annihilate This Week is a single by American hardcore punk band Black Flag. It contains songs from&quot; Who&#x27;s Got the 10½?&quot; The cover, which features numerous items of drug paraphernalia, was banned in some record stores.

==Track listing==
Side one
#&quot;Annihilate This Week&quot; (Ginn) – 4:14

Side two
#&quot;Best One Yet&quot; (Roessler/Rollins) – 2:35
#&quot;Sinking&quot; (Ginn/Rollins) – 5:04

==Personnel==
* Henry Rollins – vocals
* Greg Ginn – guitar
* Kira Roessler – bass
* Anthony Martinez – drums

